<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OmniBot 後臺</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #1a1a2e; color: #eee;
      display: flex; min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .sidebar {
      width: 240px; background: #16213e; padding: 24px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    }
    .sidebar h2 { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .sidebar nav a {
      display: block; padding: 10px 14px; color: #aaa;
      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .sidebar nav a:hover { background: #0f3460; color: #fff; }
    .sidebar .logout { margin-top: auto; color: #e94560; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 14px; }
    .sidebar .logout:hover { background: rgba(233,69,96,0.1); }
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 32px; }
    h1 { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .empty { text-align: center; color: #666; padding: 40px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <h2>🤖 OmniBot 後臺</h2>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">📊 儀表板</a>
    </nav>
    <a href="/logout" class="logout">🚪 登出</a>
  </aside>
  <div class="main">
    <h1>伺服器設定</h1>
    <div class="empty">歡迎/告別頻道請透過環境變數 `WELCOME_CHANNEL_ID` 和 `FAREWELL_CHANNEL_ID` 設定</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
